import pandas as pd
import altair as alt
import numpy as np
import datetime as dt

def count_uniq(li):
	prev='nAn'
	count=0
	rez={}
	for i in li:
		if prev=='nAn':
			prev = i
			continue
		if prev==i:
			count+=1
		else:	
			rez[ prev ]= { 'day':pd.Period(prev).dayofyear, 'count':count }
			prev = i
			rez[ prev ] = { 'day':pd.Period(i).dayofyear, 'count':1 }
			count=0
	return rez




data = pd.read_csv('all_month.csv')
data = data.where(data.type=='earthquake').dropna()

new=data.time.str.split('T',n=1,expand=True)


quake_per_day=count_uniq(new[0])

qpd=pd.DataFrame.from_dict(quake_per_day,orient='index',columns=['day','count'])



alt.Chart(qpd).mark_circle(size=10).encode(x='day',y='count')

import pandas as pd
import altair as alt
import numpy as np
import datetime as dt

def count_uniq(li):
	prev='nAn'
	count=0
	rez={}
	for i in li:
		if prev=='nAn':
			prev = i
			continue
		if prev==i:
			count+=1
		else:	
			rez[ prev ]= { 'day':pd.Period(prev).dayofyear, 'count':count }
			prev = i
			rez[ prev ] = { 'day':pd.Period(i).dayofyear, 'count':1 }
			count=0
	return rez




data = pd.read_csv('all_month.csv')
data = data.where(data.type=='earthquake').dropna()

new=data.time.str.split('T',n=1,expand=True)


quake_per_day=count_uniq(new[0])

qpd=pd.DataFrame.from_dict(quake_per_day,orient='index',columns=['day','count'])



alt.Chart(qpd).mark_circle(size=10).encode(x='day',y='count')

alt.Chart(data).mark_bar().encode(
    x='mag',
    y='count()',
)
